sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Instructor
participant GradeConsole
participant GradeService
participant GradeRepository
participant GradeJson as "grades.json"


GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: loadStudents()
alt grades.json exists
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: read students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: stored student records
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: students
else file missing
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: empty student list
end
GradeConsole->>GradeService: initialize(students)
GradeService->>GradeService: set nextStudentId from loaded data
GradeService-->>GradeConsole: ready
